《'''關鍵救援72小時'''》（{{lang-en|''The Next Three Days''}}）是一部[[2010年電影列表|2010年]]上映的美国[[剧情片|剧情片]]，由[[保罗·哈吉斯|保罗·哈吉斯]]导演，[[羅素·克洛|羅素·克洛]]及[[伊莉莎白·班克斯|伊莉莎白·班克斯]]主演。翻拍自2008年的法国电影''Pour elle''<ref name="firstimpressions">{{cite news | title =First impressions that linger | work =The Age | date =March 5, 2010 | url =http://www.theage.com.au/news/entertainment/film/first-impressions-that-linger/2010/03/04/1267291918125.html?page=2 | access-date =2010-03-23 | archive-date =2015-11-24 | archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20151124122026/http://www.theage.com.au/news/entertainment/film/first-impressions-that-linger/2010/03/04/1267291918125.html?page=2 | dead-url =no }}</ref>。

